have all already started.

We deÔ¨Åne the duty cycle of the discovery schedule as:
DeÔ¨Ånition 2.1: The duty cycle of schedule Si = {si(t)| t ‚â• 0} for node ui is the percentage of time slots that ui chooses state ON :

