III. ADJUSTABLE NEIGHBOR DISCOVERY ALGORITHMS
In this section, we present two adjustable neighbor discovery algorithms that can be adopted in our framework. The Ô¨Årst one utilizes multiple primes to construct the discovery schedule, while the other one uses the quorum system for schedule construction.

